high_descs: Head towards to the fridge
Take a knife from the fridge
Head towards to the dining table
Cut the tomato into slices
Turn to the right turn to the left
Head towards to the microwave
Head towards to the microwave
Keep the knife inside the microwave
Head towards to the dining table
Take the sliced tomato from the table
Head towards to the microwave
Keep the tomato inside the microwave
Head towards to the dining table
Take another tomato from the table
Head towards to the microwave
Keep it inside the microwave
anns.task_desc: Take two tomato keep it inside the microwave

high_descs: Turn around and go to the fridge in the corner to your right.
Remove the knife from the fridge.
Turn around and go towards the dining table opposite the fridge.
Slice the tomato that is in the middle of the table, behind the bowl.
Look towards the bowl on the left that has a tomato inside it.
Slice that tomato in the bowl as well.
Turn and walk past the door on the right, heading to the platform with the microwave on it.
Place the knife inside the microwave.
Return to the table with the sliced tomatoes.
Pick up a tomato slice from the first tomato you sliced.
Go back to the microwave.
Place the tomato slice inside the microwave.
Return to the dining table again.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the second tomato you sliced.
Go back to the microwave again.
Put the second tomato slice into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Slice two tomatoes, take one slice from each and place them into a microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and go across to the fridge.
Pick up the knife from the fridge.
Turn right toward the sofa, then turn right and go to the dining table.
Slice the tomato in the middle of the dining table.
Go to the end of the dining table closer to the wall.
Slice the tomato in the plate on the dining table.
Turn around and go to the black microwave.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Head back to the dining table.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the middle of the tomato in the plate
Head back to the black microwave.
Place the tomato slice in the microwave to the left corner.
Head back to the dining table.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the middle of the tomato in the middle of the table.
Head back to the microwave.
Place the tomato slice in the microwave behind the other slice.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of tomato from two different tomatoes in the microwave.
